      <title>印尼企业 Mr DIY 计划首次公开募股，募资额高达 2.97 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/mr-diy-s-indonesian-business-ipo-seeks-up-to-297-million-in-december-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mr DIY Group (M) Bhd. 的印尼姊妹公司将通过首次公开募股在雅加达上市，旨在筹集高达 4.7 万亿卢比（2.97 亿美元），这将是该国一年多以来最大规模的上市交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/mr-diy-s-indonesian-business-ipo-seeks-up-to-297-million-in-december-listing</guid>
