    <item>
      <title>大日本印刷公司称 Elliott 已出售其大部分股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dai-nippon-printing-says-elliott-has-sold-most-of-its-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大日本印刷株式会社 (Dai Nippon Printing Co.) 表示，Elliott Investment Management 似乎大幅减持了该公司股份，而这距离该激进基金购买该公司股份还不到两年。该消息导致该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dai-nippon-printing-says-elliott-has-sold-most-of-its-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
